<plot>A biographical "mockumentary" that offers a glimpse into the life and mind of master of the macabre, director Tim Burton. It features faked home movies of Burton's idiosyncratic childhood and tongue-in-cheek interviews. Originally premiered as an HBO special to promote the release of "Edward Scissorhands"</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?262991</url></doc>
